delivered to hardness of their hearts:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.7"},["span.padWord","1 Ne."],"14:7"],";"],["li","being hard in hearts, Laman",["sup","1"],"and Lemuel look not to God for understanding:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/15.3"},["span.padWord","1 Ne."],"15:3"],";"],["li","if ye harden not hearts and ask in faith, these things shall be made known:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/15.11"},["span.padWord","1 Ne."],"15:11"],";"],["li","Jews will harden hearts against the Holy One:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.5"},["span.padWord","1 Ne."],"22:5"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/6.10"},"2 Ne. 6:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.10"},["span.padWord","2 Ne."],"25:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.15"},"Mosiah 3:15"],"; )"],["li","many harden hearts against the Holy Spirit:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.2"},"2 Ne. 33:2"],";"],["li","those of house of Israel who harden not hearts shall be saved in kingdom of God:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.4-5"},"Jacob 6:4–5"],";"],["li","people of Noah",["sup","3"],"harden hearts against Abinadi’s words:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/11.29"},"Mosiah 11:29"],";"],["li","he who hardens heart receives lesser portion of word:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.10"},"Alma 12:10"],";"],["li","whoso repenteth and hardeneth not his heart shall have claim on mercy:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.34"},["span.padWord","Alma"],"12:34"],";"],["li","let us repent and harden not our hearts lest we provoke the Lord to wrath:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.37"},["span.padWord","Alma"],"12:37"],";"],["li","men reject the Spirit because of hardness of hearts:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/13.4"},["span.padWord","Alma"],"13:4"],";"],["li","dissenters are harder than Lamanites, cause Lamanites to harden hearts:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/21.3"},["span.padWord","Alma"],"21:3"],";"],["li","enlightened people who fall into sin become more hardened:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/24.30"},["span.padWord","Alma"],"24:30"],";"],["li","if ye could be healed by merely casting about your eyes, would ye harden your hearts in unbelief and not cast about your eyes:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.21"},["span.padWord","Alma"],"33:21"],";"],["li","come forth and harden not your hearts any longer:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.31"},["span.padWord","Alma"],"34:31"],";"],["li","Nephites harden hearts in sin and iniquities:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/37.10"},["span.padWord","Alma"],"37:10"],";"],["li","the Spirit withdraws from Nephites because of hardness of hearts:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/6.35"},"Hel. 6:35"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.8"},["span.padWord","Hel."],"13:8"],"; )"],["li","because of Nephites’ hardness of heart, the Lord will withdraw his word:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.8"},["span.padWord","Hel."],"13:8"],";"],["li","people become more hardened in iniquity:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/16.12"},["span.padWord","Hel."],"16:12"],";"],["li","lyings sent forth among people by Satan to harden their hearts:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/1.22"},"3 Ne. 1:22"],";"],["li","if Gentiles harden hearts against him, the Lord will return their iniquities upon their own heads:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.28"},["span.padWord","3 Ne."],"20:28"],";"],["li","if Israel will repent and harden not hearts, the Lord will establish Church among them:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.22"},["span.padWord","3 Ne."],"21:22"],";"],["li","Mormon",["sup","2"],"prays for Nephites, but without faith because of their",["i","hardheartedness"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/3.12"},"Morm. 3:12"],";"],["li","devil hardens men’s hearts, that they murder prophets:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/8.25"},"Ether 8:25"],";"],["li","when Mormon",["sup","2"],"uses no sharpness, Nephites harden hearts against God’s word:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/9.4"},"Moro. 9:4"],";"]]],["div",{"id":"f3","uri":"/scriptures/triple-index/hardheartedness.f3","order":".000.2837"},["ul.index",["li","testimony of Three Witnesses to condemn this generation if they harden hearts:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/5.18"},"D&C 5:18"],";"],["li","Satan hardens hearts of people:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.32"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"10:32"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.63"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"10:63"],"; )"],["li","the Lord will establish Church if this generation hardens not hearts:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.53"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"10:53"],";"],["li","the Lord will gather them if they will not harden hearts:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.65"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"10:65"],";"],["li","elect hear the Lord’s voice and harden not hearts:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.7"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"29:7"],";"],["li","wicked who do not hear the Lord’s voice but harden hearts will be kept in chains:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.5-6"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"38:5–6"],";"],["li","members warned not to harden hearts:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.6"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"45:6"],";"],["li","those in darkness turn hearts from the Lord because of precepts of men:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.29"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"45:29"],";"],["li","in last days men will harden hearts against the Lord:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.33"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"45:33"],";"],["li","blindness of heart may cause man to fall:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.15"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"58:15"],";"],["li","Satan turns men’s hearts away from truth:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/78.10"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"78:10"],";"],["li","soul that hardens heart against covenant will be delivered to Satan’s buffetings:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/82.21"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"82:21"],";"],["li","children of Israel hardened hearts and could not endure the Lord’s presence:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.24"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"84:24"],";"],["li","men to be upbraided for evil hearts of unbelief:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.76"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"84:76"],";"],["li","the Lord will feel after Twelve if they harden not their hearts:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/112.13"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"112:13"],";"]]],["div",{"id":"f4","uri":"/scriptures/triple-index/hardheartedness.f4","order":".000.2838"},["ul.index",["li","hearts have waxed hard:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/6.27"},"Moses 6:27"],";"],["li","hearts of Abraham’s fathers were set to do evil:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/1.6"},"Abr. 1:6"],";"]]]]],"refs":null}
